  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2 style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/special-offers/save-100-per-couple/2022-slovenia-holidays#Lake Bled"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span></a>Visit Slovenia this Summer</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Explore Slovenia with Inghams. This alluring and incredibly diverse country is set at the foot of the spectacular peaks of the Julian Alps.  Discover its natural charms and set your sights upon snow-capped peaks, deep forests, and sparkling lakes.</span></p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/971eed069c434e59a6268833efa31aee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/971eed069c434e59a6268833efa31aee}#Lake Bled" title="Slovenia Holidays" data-anchor="#Lake Bled"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Lake Bled</span></a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/971eed069c434e59a6268833efa31aee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/971eed069c434e59a6268833efa31aee}#Kranjska Gora" title="Slovenia Holidays" data-anchor="#Kranjska Gora"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Kranjska Gora</span></a> </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089085/slovenia-lake-bled-summer-838x400.jpg" alt="Slovenia Lake Bled" data-udi="umb://media/9cf4c483332b4d26a0cd3aaf8fd8a6e0" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Make it a summer to remember and experience more with Inghams. You’ll find an endless amount of activities to enjoy, from cycling and hiking, to strolling through Slovenia's beautiful nature parks and medieval towns.</span></p>
<p><strong>Don't miss out on our limited time Slovenia savings! </strong></p>
<p><strong>Speak to a member of our UK based team on <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111</span> or book online.</strong></p>
