<p><a name="Lake Bled"></a></p>
<h3>Lake Bled</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Live a fairy tale at this picture-postcard resort with its magnificent blue lake, medieval cliff-top castle and panoramic views. Lake Bled is known as Slovenia’s most famous beauty spot and it’s not hard to see why. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The serene waters are surrounded by rolling emerald hills and the snow-capped mountains of the Julian Alps. Whether you’re hiking in one of the area’s numerous nature trails, or relaxing at one of Lake Bled’s numerous restaurants and bars, this resort offers plenty to do.</span></p>
