<p><a name="Kranjska Gora"></a></p>
<h3>Kranjska Gora</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This cultural mountain town is surrounded by beautiful landscapes and walks. A hiker's paradise, Kranjska Gora is the perfect resort for an active holiday. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You’ll find well marked trails and paths that cover the whole area, allowing you to fully enjoy the spectacular mountain scenery and unspoiled, natural beauty. For those after a more tranquil escape, then this resort offers various wellness centres making it the perfect spot to relax. </span></p>
